[{"title":"Cask 'java' is unreadable","url":"/2021/04/20/Cask-java-is-unreadable/","content":"<h1 id=\"Problem\"><a href=\"#Problem\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Problem\"></a>Problem</h1><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&gt; brew upgrade</span><br><span class=\"line\">Warning: Unexpected method <span class=\"string\">'license'</span> called on Cask java.</span><br><span class=\"line\">Follow the instructions here:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  https://github.com/Homebrew/homebrew-cask<span class=\"comment\">#reporting-bugs</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">Error: Cask <span class=\"string\">'java'</span> is unreadable: undefined method `release<span class=\"string\">' for OS::Mac:Module</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h1 id=\"Solution\"><a href=\"#Solution\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Solution\"></a>Solution</h1><h2 id=\"if-you-want-to-uninstall-java-cask\"><a href=\"#if-you-want-to-uninstall-java-cask\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"if you want to uninstall java cask\"></a>if you want to uninstall java cask</h2><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&gt; brew uninstall homebrew/cask/java; rm -rf <span class=\"string\">\"<span class=\"variable\">$(brew --prefix)</span>/Caskroom/java\"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"if-facing-no-available-formula\"><a href=\"#if-facing-no-available-formula\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"if facing no available formula\"></a>if facing no available formula</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Error: No available formula or cask with the name <span class=\"string\">\"homebrew/cask/java\"</span>.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>then install openjdk instead</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&gt; brew install openjdk</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h1 id=\"Reference\"><a href=\"#Reference\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Reference\"></a>Reference</h1><p><a href=\"https://github.com/Homebrew/discussions/discussions/113\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Vitorgalvao’s Solution</a></p>\n","tags":["brew"]},{"title":"My First Blog","url":"/2020/05/01/My-First-Blog/","content":"<h1 id=\"install-hexo\"><a href=\"#install-hexo\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"install hexo\"></a>install hexo</h1><h2 id=\"Step-by-Step\"><a href=\"#Step-by-Step\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Step-by-Step\"></a>Step-by-Step</h2><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm insntall -g hexo-cli</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo init &lt;folder&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">cd</span> &lt;folder&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">npm install</span><br><span class=\"line\">modify _config.yml</span><br><span class=\"line\">git <span class=\"built_in\">clone</span> https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next.git themes/next</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n\n<h1 id=\"set-deploy-to-github\"><a href=\"#set-deploy-to-github\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"set deploy to github\"></a>set deploy to github</h1><ol>\n<li>create <username>.github.io project</li>\n<li>npm install hexo-deployer-git –save</li>\n<li>modify _config.yml<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">deploy:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"built_in\">type</span>: git</span><br><span class=\"line\">  repo: </span><br><span class=\"line\">    github: git@github.com:&lt;username&gt;/&lt;username&gt;.github.io.git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>then you can check: username.github.io</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"upload-to-github-for-multi-pc-synchronization\"><a href=\"#upload-to-github-for-multi-pc-synchronization\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"upload to github for multi-pc synchronization\"></a>upload to github for multi-pc synchronization</h1><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git init</span><br><span class=\"line\">git checkout -b src</span><br><span class=\"line\">modify .gitignore   <span class=\"comment\">#there should have a default one</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">git add .</span><br><span class=\"line\">git submodule add https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next.git themes/next</span><br><span class=\"line\">git commit -m <span class=\"string\">\"first commit\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">git remote add origin git@github.com:wthsieh23/wthsieh23.github.io.git</span><br><span class=\"line\">git push origin src</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h1 id=\"add-SSH-public-key-to-github\"><a href=\"#add-SSH-public-key-to-github\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"add SSH public key to github\"></a>add SSH public key to github</h1><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ssh-keygen -t rsa -b 4096 -C <span class=\"string\">\"wentsan.hsieh@gmail.com\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">ssh-agent -s</span><br><span class=\"line\">ssh-add ~/.ssh/id_rsa</span><br><span class=\"line\">cat ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub  <span class=\"comment\"># copy the content and paste to github personal setting/ssh</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h1 id=\"add-categories\"><a href=\"#add-categories\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"add categories\"></a>add categories</h1><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo new page categories</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>then add type in <code>source/categories/index.md</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">---</span><br><span class=\"line\">title: categories</span><br><span class=\"line\">date: 2020-05-01 06:45:20</span><br><span class=\"line\">type: &quot;categories&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>then add the below attributes in the page you want</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">---</span><br><span class=\"line\">title: xxx</span><br><span class=\"line\">categories:</span><br><span class=\"line\">- <span class=\"built_in\">test</span>      <span class=\"comment\"># category</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">- test1     <span class=\"comment\"># subcategory</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h1 id=\"add-tags\"><a href=\"#add-tags\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"add tags\"></a>add tags</h1><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo new page tags</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>add type in <code>source/tags/index.md</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">---</span><br><span class=\"line\">title: tags</span><br><span class=\"line\">date: 2020-05-01 07:04:55</span><br><span class=\"line\">type: &quot;tags&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n\n<p>then add tags as below in the page you want</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">---</span><br><span class=\"line\">title: tags</span><br><span class=\"line\">date: 2020-05-01 07:04:55</span><br><span class=\"line\">type: &quot;tags&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h1 id=\"local-search\"><a href=\"#local-search\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"local search\"></a>local search</h1><p>install the package<br><code>npm install hexo-generator-searchdb --save</code></p>\n<p>enable the local search feature in <code>themes/next/_config.yml</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"># Local Search</span><br><span class=\"line\"># Dependencies: https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;theme-next&#x2F;hexo-generator-searchdb</span><br><span class=\"line\">local_search:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  enable: true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>add below content to blog’s <code>_config.yml</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">search:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  path: search.json</span><br><span class=\"line\">  field: post</span><br><span class=\"line\">  content: true</span><br><span class=\"line\">  format: html</span><br><span class=\"line\">  limit: 10000</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","categories":["blog"],"tags":["hexo"]},{"title":"termux","url":"/2020/05/01/termux/","content":"<h2 id=\"nodejs\"><a href=\"#nodejs\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"nodejs\"></a>nodejs</h2><p>當在 termux上，執行 <code>npm install</code> 時會 failed, 大絕招就是</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">rm -rf <span class=\"variable\">$PREFIX</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","categories":["android","termux"],"tags":["termux"]},{"title":"Hexo Commands","url":"/2021/03/16/Hexo-Commands/","content":"<h1 id=\"create-post-page-draft\"><a href=\"#create-post-page-draft\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"create post/page/draft\"></a>create post/page/draft</h1><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo new title    <span class=\"comment\"># use default_layout setting in _config.yml</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo new post title</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo new post <span class=\"string\">\"title with space\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo new draft <span class=\"string\">\"title with space\"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n\n<h1 id=\"publish-post-from-draft\"><a href=\"#publish-post-from-draft\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"publish post from draft\"></a>publish post from draft</h1><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo pulish <span class=\"string\">\"title with space\"</span>    <span class=\"comment\">#move draft content from source/_drafts to source/_posts folder</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h1 id=\"blog-generation\"><a href=\"#blog-generation\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"blog generation\"></a>blog generation</h1><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo g     <span class=\"comment\"># hexo generate</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo s     <span class=\"comment\"># hexo server</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo s -d  <span class=\"comment\"># able to view draft posts</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo d     <span class=\"comment\"># hexo deploy,   publish to github</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo g -d  <span class=\"comment\"># generate and deploy</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h1 id=\"Reference\"><a href=\"#Reference\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Reference\"></a>Reference</h1><ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.github.com/en/github/writing-on-github\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">github flavored markdown syntax</a></li>\n</ul>\n"},{"title":"Productivity","url":"/2021/04/08/Productivity/","content":"<h1 id=\"Background\"><a href=\"#Background\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Background\"></a>Background</h1><p>由於個性實在是太會拖了且做事容易發散，年輕時還可以熬夜加班來做事，但老了越來越有”心有餘而力不足”的感覺。很多想法，但執行力不夠，往往都沒法實踐。<br>認真思考該怎麼改善這狀況</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n\n<h1 id=\"執行策略\"><a href=\"#執行策略\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"執行策略\"></a>執行策略</h1><ul>\n<li>Daily Target<blockquote>\n<p>目前的想法是daily只訂2～3個”可執行且可完成”的目標來進行。</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li>工作環境簡單化<blockquote>\n<p>目前想法是能透過”SOP＋自動化”來讓”工廠運作”有效率</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li>搭配的工具<blockquote>\n<p>目前是用<a href=\"https://todoist.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"todoist website\">Todoist</a> for daily target，<a href=\"https://trello.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"trello website\">Trello</a> for long term plan。</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>今年來試著看看是不是能提升我的工作效率</p>\n","tags":["productivity"]},{"title":"tmux","url":"/2021/04/30/tmux/","content":"<h1 id=\"Panes-related\"><a href=\"#Panes-related\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Panes related\"></a>Panes related</h1><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Prefix + 指令</th>\n<th>說明</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>%</td>\n<td>垂直分割</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>“</td>\n<td>水平分割</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>o</td>\n<td>switch pane</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>方向鍵</td>\n<td>切換至指定方向</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>space</td>\n<td>切換佈局</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>!</td>\n<td>獨立建立一個window</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>x</td>\n<td>close pane</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h1 id=\"Windows-related\"><a href=\"#Windows-related\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Windows related\"></a>Windows related</h1><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Prefix + 指令</th>\n<th>說明</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>c</td>\n<td>create window</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>w</td>\n<td>select window</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>n</td>\n<td>next window</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>p</td>\n<td>previous window</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>+num</td>\n<td>switch to window-num</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&amp;</td>\n<td>close current window</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h1 id=\"Sessions-related\"><a href=\"#Sessions-related\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Sessions related\"></a>Sessions related</h1><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>指令</th>\n<th>說明</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>tmux ls</td>\n<td>list all sessions</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>tmux attach -t num</td>\n<td>attach session-num</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Prefix + 指令</th>\n<th>說明</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>$</td>\n<td>rename session</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>d</td>\n<td>detach current session</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>s</td>\n<td>select session</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>L</td>\n<td>上一個 session</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>(</td>\n<td>previous session</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>)</td>\n<td>next session</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h1 id=\"Search\"><a href=\"#Search\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Search\"></a>Search</h1><p>Prefix + 指令|說明<br>f|search keyword in all windows</p>\n<p>more information</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">man tmux</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>—|—</p>\n","tags":["tmux"]}]